---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import '@/styles/pages/whats-new.css';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Shopping Mall Receipt Converter"
  description=""
  canonicalUrl="https://www.formx.ai/tools/shopping-mall-receipt-converter"
>
  <section class="title-2 bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer pagetitle__container mt-60 w-container">
      <h1 class="pricing-title mb-0">
        <span class="heading-gradient">Effortlessly Extract Data from Receipts with&#x2028;<br />&#x200d;</span>Our Free OCR Receipt Scanner
      </h1>
      <p class="section__header__content mb-40">Try our free OCR receipt scanner (test converter) and see how FormX.ai&#x2028;can turn your receipts into usable data!</p>
      <div class="w-embed w-iframe">
        <iframe src="https://widgets.formx.ai/shopping-mall-receipt/" style="width: 100%; height: 600px" frameBorder="0"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section product-section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper m-reverse">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/pages/converter_privacy.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" />
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">Your Data.<br />Your Privacy.<br />Our Promise.</h2>
          <div class="product-2-block-paragraph">We prioritize user privacy and delete your data after processing your Shopping Mall Receipt with OCR.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_features@2x.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            width="600"
            sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px"
            alt=""
            srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_features@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_features@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_features@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_features@2x.webp 1370w"
            class="image-rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-content-wrapper">
        <div class="product-heading-wrapper mw-80">
          <h2 class="product-heading">What is OCR Receipt Scanning?</h2>
          <div class="product-subheading">OCR receipt scanning is a technology that uses Optical Character Recognition to extract text from images of receipts.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-content-wrapper">
          <div class="_3-block-grid">
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 pb-32">
              <div class="card-svg-block">
                <img src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-upload@2x.webp" loading="lazy" width="80" sizes="(max-width: 1279px) 80px, (max-width: 1439px) 6vw, 80px" alt="" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-upload@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-upload@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-upload@2x.webp 810w" class="card-svg full-width image-rounded" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper px-16">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Uploading a receipt image</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">You can either take a photo of your receipt or upload a scanned image.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 pb-32">
              <div class="card-svg-block">
                <img src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-ocr@2x.webp" loading="lazy" width="80" sizes="(max-width: 1279px) 80px, (max-width: 1439px) 6vw, 80px" alt="" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-ocr@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-ocr@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-ocr@2x.webp 810w" class="card-svg full-width image-rounded" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper px-16">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">OCR analysis</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">The OCR software analyzes the image and tries to identify the characters and words.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 pb-32">
              <div class="card-svg-block">
                <img src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-export@2x.webp" loading="lazy" width="80" sizes="(max-width: 1279px) 80px, (max-width: 1439px) 6vw, 80px" alt="" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-export@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-export@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_whatis-export@2x.webp 810w" class="card-svg full-width image-rounded" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper px-16">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Data extraction</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">Once the characters are recognized, the software extracts the relevant data, such as the merchant name, purchase date, total amount, and itemized list.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default heading-content w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-wrapper mx-auto mb-60 max-width-800">
        <h2 class="product-heading">When Do You Need OCR Receipt Scanning?</h2>
        <div class="product-subheading">OCR receipt scanning can be a valuable tool in various scenarios, including:</div>
      </div>
      <div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="_2-block-flex tabs-with-image w-tabs">
        <div class="hover-change tabs w-tab-menu">
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Personal finance management</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Track your expenses and income by automatically extracting&#x2028;data from receipts.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Accounting and bookkeeping</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Simplify the process of recording transactions by importing&#x2028;data directly from receipts.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Business expense reporting</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Easily submit expense reports to your employer by scanning&#x2028;and extracting relevant information from receipts.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 4" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Research and analysis</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Analyze spending patterns and trends by extracting&#x2028;data from a large number of receipts.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 5" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Data entry automation</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Reduce manual data entry tasks and improve efficiency by&#x2028;automating the process of extracting information from receipts.</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="_2-block-flex-image tabs w-tab-content">
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-personal@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-personal@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-personal@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-personal@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-personal@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="100vw" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-accounting@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-accounting@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-accounting@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-accounting@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-accounting@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-reporting@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-reporting@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-reporting@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-reporting@2x.webp 1200w" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-reporting@2x.webp" loading="eager" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 4" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="100vw" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-analysis@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-analysis@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-analysis@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-analysis@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-analysis@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 5" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="100vw" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-data@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_shopping_when-data@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-data@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-data@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_shopping_when-data@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-content-wrapper">
        <div class="product-heading-wrapper mw-800px">
          <h2 class="product-heading">Accuracy of OCR Receipt Scanning and&#x2028;<span class="heading-gradient"><br />How FormX.ai Achieves High Results</span></h2>
          <div class="product-subheading">OCR receipt scanning accuracy can be affected by image quality and receipt formats. However, FormX.ai uses advanced technology to deliver highly accurate results.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-content-wrapper">
          <div class="grid-12 row-gap-60 rows-1">
            <div id="w-node-_4f1db2a9-0cb0-338e-8ac4-da617c0a309f-04883da9" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 m-16 bordered first">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">1</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Advanced OCR engine</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">We utilize a powerful OCR engine specifically trained on a massive dataset of receipts. This allows it to recognize a wide range of fonts, layouts, and printing styles commonly found on receipts.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="w-node-_43688fa3-aba8-c30c-31a3-6a8978c29102-04883da9" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 m-16 bordered first">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">2</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Machine learning</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">We leverage machine learning algorithms to continuously improve our OCR engine's accuracy. As more data is processed, the system learns to better identify and extract information from receipts.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="w-node-_4f1db2a9-0cb0-338e-8ac4-da617c0a30a8-04883da9" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 m-16">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">3</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Pre-processing and post-processing</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">Our system employs image pre-processing techniques to enhance the clarity of scanned receipts before applying OCR. Additionally, post-processing techniques are used to refine the extracted data and minimize errors.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section whats-new">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-default w-container">
      <div class="whats-new-last-section">
        <div class="whats-new-content-wrap">
          <h2 class="whats-new-last-section-heading color-white">Unlock Powerful Data Extraction with FormX.ai Solutions</h2>
          <div class="color-white">Looking to streamline your data processing beyond receipts? FormX.ai offers a suite of intelligent document processing (IDP) solutions designed to automate data extraction from various documents.</div>
        </div>
        <a href="/talk-with-us" class="button-primary button-white w-button">Learn more about FormX.ai's Retail Solution -&gt;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
